asset.hookText:
http://www.PFIWestern.com - The First episode of RFDTV's "On The Way To Branson" is a 30 min show hosted by PBR's Justin Mckee featuring PFI Town in Springfield, MO with:

PFI Western Wear Store " America's Western Store"
With over 20,000 pairs of cowboy boots and a huge selection of western wear www.pfiwestern.com

PFI's Saddle City
One of the largest TUcker Saddle dealers in the world with over 500 saddles and everything under the sun for your horse

Beth Cross from Ariat Boots talk about how they have how to make the cowboy boot more durable, more flexable and more comfortable

Plus St James WInery and PFI's Diamond RIdge Market where you can sample cheeses and wines all dayt long.
